 a ver si podemos divertirnos.

83
00:08:47,944 --> 00:08:50,071
¿Esto te parece divertido?

84
00:08:53,283 --> 00:08:54,451
Saludos.

85
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:58,830
¡Sonríe!

86
00:09:00,832 --> 00:09:02,125
Me hago reír.

87
00:09:09,549 --> 00:09:11,551
La foto ha salido genial, Mav.

88
00:09:11,551 --> 00:09:13,345
Debería ser fotógrafo.

89
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,722
Cougar, ya no te sigue nadie.

90
00:09:15,722 --> 00:09:17,640
